// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-1391 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: 92725202-3a6f-5e2b-ad64-6940b78fac39

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:12.04*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:12.10*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:13.04*")
